            "title": "粵投發盈喜 料去年盈利漲約43%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">粵海投資(00270)發盈喜，預期2025年度歸屬公司所有者溢利約31.42億元，按年增長約43%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"粵海投資官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/00270-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"粵海投資官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/00270-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">粵海投資官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該公司指出，去年盈利提升，主要受惠兩方面。其一是去年初公司完成以實物分派粵海置地(00124)股份以支持特別股息，粵海置地業績毋須再合併於粵投報表內。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">其次則是去年在淨財務費用及行政費用節省下，粵投本身持續經營業務利潤有所增長。粵投預期，公司2025年度業績將在3月底前公布。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15620869-%e7%b2%b5%e6%8a%95%e7%99%bc%e7%9b%88%e5%96%9c-%e6%96%99%e5%8e%bb%e5%b9%b4%e7%9b%88%e5%88%a9%e6%bc%b2%e7%b4%8443",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/00270.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-29 08:22:48",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
